8.421 is an advanced course in
atomic physics-- graduate level

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:40.430
course.

00:00:40.430 --> 00:00:46.230
8.421 is part of a new semester
sequence in atomic physics.

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:54.550
Actually, 8.421 is taken
first in this sequence

00:00:54.550 --> 00:00:58.960
