where we have some variable

00:42:38.670 --> 00:42:44.540
and it varies periodically.

00:42:44.540 --> 00:42:53.670
So in other words, yes,
there is a variable,

00:42:53.670 --> 00:42:54.780
which an be anything.

00:42:54.780 --> 00:42:57.900
It can be the population
of quantum state.

00:42:57.900 --> 00:42:59.370
It can be an electric field.

00:42:59.370 --> 00:43:01.900
It can be the
position of an atom.

00:43:01.900 --> 00:43:03.790
It can be anything
you can think about

00:43:03.790 --> 00:43:05.930
and anything you can measure.

00:43:05.930 --> 00:43:14.250
And if this variable
the varies periodically,

00:43:14.250 --> 00:43:16.710
you have a resonance.

00:43:16.710 --> 00:43:19.840
Of course, the periodic
variation usually

00:43:19.840 --> 00:43:22.900
