drive the system.

00:43:22.900 --> 00:43:26.350
So you first drive it.

00:43:26.350 --> 00:43:27.740
And then the system oscillates.

00:43:31.030 --> 00:43:41.930
And this means now that when
you drive the system-- so this

00:43:41.930 --> 00:43:43.590
maybe a free oscillation.

00:43:43.590 --> 00:43:50.505
But now you drive the system
with a variable frequency.

00:43:53.500 --> 00:43:59.760
And what you then observe
is you observe a peak.

00:43:59.760 --> 00:44:02.950
So the phenomenon
of resonance is

00:44:02.950 --> 00:44:05.770
that you have something
which can periodically vary.

00:44:05.770 --> 00:44:15.580
And when you drive it,
you see peaked response

00:44:15.580 --> 00:44:18.895
when driven with a
variable frequency.

